    "name": "said-001-empty-envelope",
    "description": "SAID computation for the minimal envelope: schema-required fields only, no cargo, no provenance, no ownership transitions. This is the degenerate case used to verify that an implementation handles the canonical-CBOR + BLAKE3-256 pipeline on a payload with no application data.",
